# Split Expense App

A simple web app to split expenses among friends.

🚀 Live Demo: https://navaira16.github.io/split-expense-app/ 
📂 GitHub Repo: https://github.com/Navaira16/Navaira16
---

## ✨ Features
- Add expenses
- Equal split calculation
- Shows who owes and who gets back
- Dark mode

---

## 🧠 Learning Approach
Built using a vibe coding approach focusing on UI and logic building.
